title: Thai Square
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Dedicated vegetarian dishes offered on the back of the menu, which are mainly vegan and include several tofu dishes. You can book in advance and tell them you are vegan, but it is not necessary. The drinks menu includes virgin non-alcoholic cocktails. Other items on the menu can be made vegan. A part of a small chain of restaurants in the UK; this one being quite large with two entrances, one on Thames St and one on River St.
